{"tid":788061,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"放大假/去旅行關你地班仆街同事咩事","createTime":"2018-08-21T07:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T11:23:05.000Z","uid":107733,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5bb4d5e3ac2389ec4f57fba131097a6ece3b4e","tid":788061,"uid":107733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母問問問<br />\n放大假關你撚事，又問去邊又話諗下有咩買<br />\n屌你同你好撚熟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我放假都要同你買野，係你工人呀？<br />\n你話你係我老闆我就話諗下啫<br />\n屌你個撚個老撚奉幫手買野<br />\n唔該你地唔好再咁on9<br />\n我放假無必要同你地交代<br />\n無必要幫你買乜買物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街同事又要叫人買野唔該自動收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dab33415b93496caad47761e64a6ad3bfc4325d","tid":788061,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"放假係要交代既<br />\n佢地都要plan下 幾時拎假既"},{"pid":"686d30cd782c786484baeb1ea47e947074ae8b28","tid":788061,"uid":107733,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:41:48.000Z","msg":"買手信返黎俾你班仆街食係人情<br />\n唔撚買係道理 你班仆街同事聽清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d6856b86a6b12ee16cafd2e81eeff6d3817941","tid":788061,"uid":107733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dab33415b93496caad47761e64a6ad3bfc4325d","tid":788061,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"放假係要交代既<br />\n佢地都要plan下 幾時拎假既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"交代放假，唔係交代去邊做乜買野囉"},{"pid":"0bef8a5630aaee10dbfeabddee80474bc84be579","tid":788061,"uid":56940,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出發前答好